   Tax Relief
     When President Bush sat down with House Republican Leaders this past
   spring, there was one common objective we all sought - tax relief for
   every tax paying American. When this common-sense legislation was
   passed this past May, $1.35 trillion in tax relief went back to the
   American public
   Read More...

   Defending our Nation
