   Energy Policy
     As the United States faces its greatest national energy shortage
   since the oil embargoes of the early 1970s, the Congress must promote a
   thorough and environmentally sound energy plan...

   Read More...

   Education Reform
     This January President Bush signed into law a historical reform of
   our nations education system. This bi-partisan package reforms our
   nation's schools and gives children all over our country new hope for
   their futures...

   Read More...




